<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.7.1">
<l>cīla millāc ciṟiya ṉēluñ ceyviṉai yōperitāṉ</l>
<l>ñāla muṇṭāy ñāṉamūrtti nārāya ṇāveṉ ṟeṉṟu</l>
<l>kālan tōṟum yāṉiruntu kaitalai pūca liṭṭāl</l>
<l>kōla mēṉi kāṇa vārāy kūviyuṅ koḷḷāyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even though I am [only] a little one without training/discipline, karma I made, ah, it is big.</l>
<l>If, saying [and] saying “You who have swallowed the world, Nārāyaṇa with the form of knowledge”,</l>
<l>If I sit every time [and] put with [my] hands decorations in [your] place(?),</l>
<l>you don’t come so that I see [your] beautiful body, although I call – take [it].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
